section.section:
A notice shall contain:
A legally sufficient description and any available street address of the real property subject to the covenant;
The name and address of the owner of the fee simple interest in the real property, the Department, and the holder if other than the Department;
A statement that the covenant, amendment, or termination is available in a registry at the Department, including the method of any electronic access; and
A statement that the notice is notification of an environmental covenant executed pursuant to this subtitle.
